          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1627381241266-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the onion has softened, add your <strong>beluga lentils</strong> to the onion with 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>flour</strong> and a generous grind of<strong> pepper</strong></p><p>Increase the heat to medium-high and cook for 1-2 min</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1627381251788-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1627381251788-x400.jpg",
