            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Dust your work surface with a generous sprinkling of<strong> flour</strong></p><p>Unwrap your <strong>puff</strong> <strong>pastry</strong> and roll it out to approx. 0.5cm thickness with a <strong>rolling</strong> <strong>pin</strong> and cut into 1 rectangle per person</p><p>Transfer the <strong>pastry</strong> to a <strong>non-stick baking paper</strong>-lined baking tray (or two!), then score a 1cm border around the edge of the pastry with a knife</p><p>Crimp the borders with a fork and put the tray[s] in the oven for 15 min or until puffed up and golden – this is your<strong> pie lid</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
